{"tid":1366733,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Silicon Lottery 開始挑選體質優良的 AMD Ryzen 3rd 再高價販售！","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:32:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca513b735bc522bda234d61d903784a5b25346e","tid":1366733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"Silicon Lottery 是一間專門挑選出好超的 CPU 然後賣你比較高價錢的公司，如保超 5.1 GHz 的 Core i9-9900K，現在針對 AMD Ryzen 三代他們也進行了挑選，不過目前僅有 Ryzen 7、Ryzen 9 高階，包括了 Ryzen 7 3700X、3800X 和 Ryzen 9 3900X，另外更高等級的 Ryzen 9 3950X 將於 9月推出。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.coolaler.com.tw/image/news/19/06/amd_ryzen_9_box.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F19%2F06%2Famd_ryzen_9_box.jpg&h=f8f91210&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coolaler.com/threads/silicon-lottery-amd-ryzen.356212/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolaler.com%2Fthreads%2Fsilicon-lottery-amd-ryzen.356212%2F&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9xzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=e2eef78b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coolaler.com/threads/silicon-lottery-amd-ryzen.356212/</a>"},{"pid":"5b472f2817185259c01537d786e1b959b2c3733b","tid":1366733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"其實對於一般玩家來說更重要的是他們公布的 Ryzen 三代超頻頻率以及所需電壓，如果您手上的可以在該電壓達成該時脈那體質應該是不錯的，以下是頻率、電壓以及售價。<br />\n<br />\nRyzen 7 3700X<br />\n4.05 GHz @ 1.237 V，300美元<br />\n4.10 GHz @ 1.25 V，320美元<br />\n4.15 GHz @ 1.26 V，340美元<br />\n<br />\nRyzen 7 3800X<br />\n4.20 GHz @ 1.275 V，370美元<br />\n4.25 GHz @ 1.287 V，430美元<br />\n4.30 GHz @ 1.300 V，610美元<br />\n<br />\nRyzen 9 3900X<br />\n4.00 GHz @ 1.200 V，470美元<br />\n4.05 GHz @ 1.212 V，500美元<br />\n4.10 GHz @ 1.225 V，530美元<br />\n4.15 GHz @ 1.237 V，590美元<br />\n4.20 GHz @ 1.25 V，810美元"},{"pid":"06854273b31804a3e8c42721481f38f4dc11b0d3","tid":1366733